HEADWORD: Atomicity
<hw>At`o*mic"i*ty</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>atomicit⟦eacute⟧</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>Degree of
